  <div class="section">
    <p style="color:#94a3b8;font-size:.85rem;margin-bottom:12px">将JSON Schema转换为Zod验证模式代码，支持完整的类型映射、嵌套对象、数组、枚举等。一键复制TypeScript代码。</p>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label>JSON Schema输入</label>
      <textarea id="schemaInput" placeholder="在此粘贴JSON Schema..." style="min-height:200px;font-family:'Fira Code',monospace;font-size:.82rem">{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "name": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 },
    "age": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 0 },
    "email": { "type": "string", "format": "email" },
